      "text": [
        "114 - وَقَالَ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ: «اَلسِّوَاكُ شَطْرُ اَلْوُضُوءِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.114 - Imam Ali ibn Abi Talib (as) said: \"Siwak (tooth cleaning) is half of wudu (ablution).\""
        ]
      }
